    <h2>UrGameReviews</h2>
    
    <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/5d/ca/87/5dca87b6088664ae9fa8080986a58b4c.png" width="230" , height="200">

    <p>Welcome to UrGameReviews. We are a pair of high schoolers that want to see what people really think of certain
        games. We know that you can see it on sites like <a href="https://www.metacritic.com/">Metacritic</a> and <a
            href="https://store.steampowered.com/">Steam</a>. But we want to know what the "hardcore" gamers think about
        the games they have played.</p>

    <p>Of course we won't be able to get all of the games on the site. We just don't have the time for that. At the
        moment, we only have the games on here that we find interesting, eacht of us also put one of our reviews out
        there. We also don't have all the features because we are only a team of 2 and this is our first real project.
    </p>

